ontA.label: Cohort (Metadata)
ontA.comment: An ontological representation of the Cohort parameters. The ontology has been automatically generated based on the uploaded Excel Document with Cohort Metadata (extracted on Date: 2019-08-19). This document has been also automatically generated based on the data recorded about 340 patients. For each patient, there are 438 Fields (Parameters aka Properties), the value of which often come from one out of 319 different controlled Set of Terms. Metadata extracted have been revised by technical experts (in close collaboration with clinical experts).

ontB.label: HarmonicSS - Reference Model and Vocabularies
ontB.comment:
This ontology specifies the parameters of particular interest for the diagnosis, control and/or treatment of patients associated with the primary Sjogren Syndrome (pSS). 

The design of the ontology was driven by the documents with the minimum and maximum pSS parameters (D.4.1 revised) prepared by the Clinical Partners participating in the HarmonicSS project.
